<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>١ - شعبة عن أبي إسحاق به.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>أخرجه الطبري <span class="c2">(٨٥١ و٨٥٢)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>٢ - مِسْعَر بن كِدَام.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
